data.description: Whether you're a first-time homeowner or seeking a cozy downsized haven, this inviting home offers the ideal backdrop for creating cherished memories. Move-in ready and eagerly awaiting your arrival, this cottage-style gem seamlessly combines modern comforts w/original charm. Key upgrades encompass a state-of-the-art A/C system, and a dreamy kitchen boasting upgraded stainless steel appliances. Unwind by your private salt water pool, freshly remarcited and outfitted with new pool equipment. 3rd bedroom is small and would be best used as an office. A detached garage holds your laundry and pool equipment. Great investment opportunity.
